This module exists as an alias module for org.netbeans.libs.jna. The NetBeans
module works correctly in an OSGI environment if a dependency is declared on the
packages (Import-Package). It does not work if the OSGI module used the upstream
bundle name "com.sun.jna" to import the whole bundle.

This module reexports the JNA packages under the original bundle name and version.
